description.fullDescription: Nova 2 Lite is an advanced multimodal reasoning model that intelligently balances performance and efficiency by dynamically adjusting reasoning depth based on task complexity. With flexible controls for developers to adjust the reasoning process, Nova 2 Lite delivers superior results for agentic workflows across software development, consumer experiences and enterprise applications.
description.shortDescription: Nova 2 Lite is an advanced multimodal model geared towards adaptive reasoning, efficient thinking, customization and agentic workflows.
description.supportedLanguages: Supports 200+ languages. Optimized for English, German, Spanish, French, Italian, Japanese, Korean, Arabic, Simplified Chinese, Russian, Hindi, Portuguese, Dutch, Turkish, and Hebrew
description.supportedUseCases: Image, Text, Video, Documents and Agentic AI

description.fullDescription: Embed-v4.0 is a multilingual multimodal embedding model. It is capable of transforming different modalities such as images, texts, and interleaved images and texts into a single vector representation. Embed-v4.0 offers state-of-the-art performance across all modalities (texts, images, interleaved texts and image) and in both English and multilingual settings. Embed-v4.0 offers a variety of ways for compression both on the number of dimensions and the number-format precision. The model offers byte and binary quantization and matryoshka embeddings for further compression.
description.shortDescription: Transform multiple modalities, such as texts and images, into numerical vectors.
description.supportedLanguages: Arabic, Mandarin, English, French, German, Italian, Spanish, Japanese, Korean, Portuguese
description.supportedUseCases: Text to a single embeddings Image to a single embeddings Interleaved text and images to a single embedding For E-commerce, a product consists of multiple text components (e.g. title, description, etc.) and images (i.e. different views) will be represented in a single vector.
description.unsupportedUseCases: For information, refer to the EULA.

description.fullDescription: DeepSeek-V3.1 is a hybrid model that supports both thinking and non-thinking modes. Built upon DeepSeek-V3.1-Base, which extends the original V3 checkpoint, this upgrade delivers improvements in multiple areas. The model features enhanced tool calling capabilities for superior performance in agent-based tasks, while thinking-mode maintains answer quality comparable to DeepSeek-R1-0528 with improved response times.
description.shortDescription: DeepSeek-V3.1 is a hybrid model that supports both thinking and non-thinking modes.
description.supportedUseCases: Text-to-text, science and math reasoning tasks, code generation
